<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Safari Oasis</title>
    <style>
        .back{
            font-size: 27px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: black;
        }
        .paragraph{
            font-size: 25px;
        }
        .back:hover{
            color: rgb(37, 37, 37);
        }
        .translation-btn-usa{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1300px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .paragraph{
                font-size: 25px;
                width: 280vw;
            }
        }
        .translation-btn-ro{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1390px;
        }
        .invisible{
            display: none;
            top: -1000000px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <a class="back" href="/hurghada/home">     <p class="back">←</p>    </a>
    <div class="translation">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_the_United_States.svg.png" class="translation-btn-usa" id="translation-btn-usa">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_Romania.svg.png" class="translation-btn-ro" id="translation-btn-ro">
    </div>
    <h1>Safari Oasis</h1>
    <p id="paragraph-ro" class="paragraph">
        Plimbare cu ATV-ul, 40 miute  plimbare cu bugie (2 locuri),15 minute plimbare cu camila, vizita cu JEEP-ul la Satul Beduin,20minute dus si 20 minute intors  bally dance, spectacolul focului, tanura(dans traditional egiptean) cina . 
        Plecarea  va fi in jurul orei 12: 15 in functie de hotelul unde sunteti cazati iar sosirea in jurul orei 19 : 00 in functie de hotelul unde sunteti cazati si de trafic.
        <br><br>
        Pret:<br>
        Adult: 25 €<br>
        Copil: 13 €<br><br>
        Cand:<br>
        in fiecare zi
    </p>
    <p id="paragraph-usa" class="paragraph invisible">
        ATV ride, 40 min buggy ride (2 seats), 15 minute camel ride, JEEP visit to Bedouin Village, 20 minutes round trip 20 minutes bally dance, fire show, tanura (traditional Egyptian dance) dinner .
        Departure will be around 12:15 depending on the hotel where you are staying and arrival around 19:00 depending on the hotel where you are staying and traffic.        <br><br>
        Price:<br>
        Adult: 25 €<br>
        Children: 13 €
        <br><br>
        When:<br>
        every day
    </p>
</body>
<script>
    const translateBtnUsa = document.getElementById("translation-btn-usa")
    const translateBtnRo = document.getElementById("translation-btn-ro")
    const paragraphUsa = document.getElementById("paragraph-usa")
    const paragraphRo = document.getElementById("paragraph-ro")

    translateBtnUsa.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.remove("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.add("invisible")
    })

    translateBtnRo.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.add("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.remove("invisible")
    })

</script>
</html>